{
  "stem": "7282.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 28.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we took a train from there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I didn't care where I'm going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's no--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--still in --still in 1941?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, still in 1941--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in Shepetivka?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, so you just--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I didn't care where I'm going--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--just, just to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was two trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, I mean, people, I mean, said one to the other, I mean, this train goes to Dnepropetrovsk.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This goes to Kiev, what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I sit down in a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- a train, it was a freight train, a open-- or what.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I sit down there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm waiting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, sometimes we used to wait, four, five, sometimes a day, and two days, on the-- on the train.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And during that time, you got to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody was feeding us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we run out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- still was Russian there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was stores open-- some stores was open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And to get a piece of bread, or what, you got to stay there in the line maybe for half a day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sometimes we stood there for half a day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when it comes to the end, we didn't get it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's run out, or what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So while I was sitting there at the train with my nephew, someone, a former girlfriend, and, and now, the future wife, or what, she went with her parents.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we didn't know from each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They left without me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I left without them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this, by chance, or what-- they had to go on another-- to another train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they got into our train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we met there, or what.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from there, we went, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like-- we went in Shepetivka.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the, the Germans start to bombard the, the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
